data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
You must have a legitamate, official Apple Install Disk to use this program
I do not respect those who obtain it illegally, so buy it!
Use this software safely, but use it at your own risk!
This next step will make a backup of the ISO you have made in the /var/OSXBackup.iso It will also mount the image as read-write, you must have HFS+ mounting capability
YOU MUST RUN THIS IN ROOT!
Make sure you have as much free space as your ISO, otherwise this program will crash!
